sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP Client
    participant Server as Argo Server<br/>2746/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as Workflow Controller<br/>Metrics: 9090/TCP
    participant StepPod as Step Pod + argoexec<br/>Sidecar
    participant S3 as S3/Artifact Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>Server: POST /api/v1/workflows/{ns}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / SSO<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Server->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: Workflow created<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Step Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>StepPod: Pod scheduled & started

    Note over StepPod,S3: argoexec handles artifacts

    StepPod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key/IAM<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>StepPod: Artifact data
    Note over StepPod: Execute workflow step container
    StepPod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key/IAM<br/>TLS 1.2+
    StepPod->>K8sAPI: Report status/outputs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: Pod completed

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Workflow status<br/>Schedule next step(s)

    Note over Controller,DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archive (Optional)

    Controller->>DB: Persist workflow record<br/>Auth: Username/Password<br/>Optional TLS
    Server->>DB: Query archived workflows<br/>Auth: Username/Password<br/>Optional TLS
    DB-->>Server: Archive results

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 3: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch CronWorkflow CRs
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: CronWorkflow spec (cron schedule)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR on schedule<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
